        a                        fabio:Figure ;
        dc:description           "FIG. 7. Various insect inclusions. A. AMNH WH-12, with legs from a roach (Blattodea), and the legs and distal portions of two wings from a caddisfly (Trichoptera). B. AMNH LC-A4, nymph of Heteroptera (Hemiptera). C, D. AMNH LC-B6, nymphal thrips (Thysanoptera), habitus (C) and detail of antennae (D). E. AMNH WH-3, with inclusion of entire male Chironomidae: Tanypodinae, and juvenile spider." ;
        fabio:hasRepresentation  "https://zenodo.org/record/4598585/files/figure.png" .

